Certainly! Below are some usage examples based on the provided TypeScript definitions for the Firebase Performance Monitoring Web SDK. ### Example 1: Initialize Firebase Performance Monitoring

```typescript
import { initializeApp } from '@firebase/app';
import { initializePerformance, PerformanceSettings } from '@firebase/performance';

