Sure! Here are some usage examples based on the TypeScript definitions you provided for the Firebase Realtime Database:

### Example 1: Initialize Firebase and Get Database Reference

```typescript
import { initializeApp } from '@firebase/app';
import { getDatabase, ref, set } from '@firebase/database';

// Initialize Firebase
const firebaseConfig = {
  apiKey: "YOUR_API_KEY",
  authDomain: "YOUR_AUTH_DOMAIN",
  databaseURL: "YOUR_DATABASE_URL",
  projectId: "YOUR_PROJECT_ID",
